 A campaign video sees Dr Vivek Murthy and the Sesame Street favourite go through the process of getting vaccinated and explaining to children why it is so .
In what appears to be a direct response to anti-vaccination campaigners , Elmo and Dr Murthy questions why everybody does not get a shot .
The campaign videos have been released in the wake of a measles outbreak that started at Disneyland in December , sickened 147 people in the U.S. .